{"tid":1970827,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"SAMSUNG 宣佈 S Voice 服務將於6月1 日停止","createTime":"2020-04-13T12:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T18:19:42.000Z","uid":50534,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1db4011f3ad974f179dee78d745e877e8a54b0de","tid":1970827,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"﻿ SAMSUNG 宣佈 S Voice 服務將於6月1 日停止    ,\t 2020-04-13  MobileMagazine &raquo; 最新消息 &raquo; 手機資訊 &raquo; 新料速報 &raquo; SAMSUNG 宣佈 S Voice 服務將於6月1 日停止  由於 Samsung 於 2017 年推出了全新的版本的語音助手Bixby 來取代舊版的S Voice語音助手，所以 Samsung 近日對外宣布，將在6月1日起正式暫停S Voice的服務！       有用開SAMSUNG Galaxy 手機的網友都有印像，SAMSUNG 曾於 2012 年時為了抗衡APPLE 語音助手 Siri，推出了自家語音助手 S Voice。不過這個 S Voice 未能完全滿足用戶的需求，所以 SAMSUNG 於2017 年推出 Bixby 來取代，而近日 SAMSUNG 對外宣佈，將於6月1日起暫停S Voice的服務。    據 Samsung 指出，受影響的設備就包括了Galaxy A3/A9/S7/S6等多款舊設備、以及Galaxy Watch、Gear S/S2/S3等多款可穿戴設備將受到影響，不過 Samsung 於在文稿最後表示，這些用戶可以升級至最新的Bixby軟件來代替 S Voice。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2020/04/samsung-s-voice-61.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2F2020%2F04%2Fsamsung-s-voice-61.html&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=a329f41b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2020/04/samsung-s-voice-61.html</a>"},{"pid":"1b594c01bebf9c3c874fe0f9c68f6ca33ccbb4b5","tid":1970827,"uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"語音助手除咗Google，其他都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73381f1128b6d0b924a1a06dc8cd8b704e217e8","tid":1970827,"uid":52311,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b594c01bebf9c3c874fe0f9c68f6ca33ccbb4b5","tid":1970827,"uid":109923,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"語音助手除咗Google，其他都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"語音助手 直頭ON居"}